## Performance Targets

- **Bundled icons**: < 10ms render time
- **Cached icons**: < 50ms render time
- **First fetch**: < 500ms (with Iconify API)
- **Cache memory**: < 50MB for typical app
- **Bundle size**: < 2MB even with 500 production icons

